  "description": "Self-hosted torrent pipeline observability for the library service (workstream raw-jp, milestone v0.2). Covers the queue (job status counts + status mix), the worker pool (active torrents, seeding torrents), throughput (library_download_bytes_total rate), disk pressure (library_disk_free_bytes), and enqueue rejects (library_enqueue_rejected_total by reason). All metrics emitted by services/library/internal/metrics/library_metrics.go.",
